{
 - Some warnings:
    -  Diferent quotes support only in "Fixed Templates":
        Examples of different quotes:
                   [catalog].[schema].(table)
                   <c:catalog>.<s:schema>.<t:table>
    - "Fixed Templates" do not allowed change Quote at runtime.
       "Fixed tamplate" marked as:
         ...
         QuoteTemplate :#0
